  m_text: "   -Added Crafting\n   -Added Visitation\n   -Added Custom Visitors\n  
    -Added Help Text in the Map \n     Editor\n   -Added Generators\n   -Added Contraband
    \n     Detectors\n   -Added Ziplines\n   -Added Colored Item Tooltips\n   -Added
    Items Spawning\n   -Added Shadows\n   -Added Correct NPC Turning\n   -Added Toilets\n  
    -Added TVs\n   -Added Quitting\n   -Added Escaping\n   -Added Custom Desks\n  
    -Added Payphones\n   -Added Signs\n   -Added All Objects Spawning\n   -Removed
    the Options Menu\n   -Added Music and Sounds to \n     the Main Menu and Map
    \n     Editor\n   -Added Opening Logo \n     Sequence\n   -Removed Test Prisons\n  
    -Added Test Prison\n   -Added Center Perks\n   -Added Warning Text Boxes\n  
    -Added Dust and Particles\n   -Removed Roof Falling for \n     Testing\n   -Added
    Bed Dummy Placing\n   -Added Bed Sheet Placing\n   -Added Healing\n   -Added
    Insta-KO\n   -Changed Zone Deletion and \n     Movement\n   -Squashed Bugs"
